Phoenix::

"Pumpskin's taking care of him," Phoenix reassures her as she carries 
her toward the base.  "Try to relax."  The femme decides to try a 
little trick her father Skyblaze taught her.  Closing her eyes, she 
lets the energy of her mutant spark well up naturally, transmitting a 
soothing warmth through her into Starstorm.  The power deadens the 
pain and recharges the dragon bot's systems a bit.
